channel.title: Big drop party
channel.description:
I just remembered I had a repeat membership on RS. Since I don't play anymore, that's just wasting my money.
I logged in just for the hell of it, and saw how terrible it was. Since I do have a large cash pile, I want to drop a bit of it for fun, maybe 100m or so in needles or cabbages at the drop room and a few rares.
Anyone else willing to jump in with the needle idea..(as in saying like 300m drop party) but it's all needles.
